# Pure compile (no compile-server). Cold js compile is ~3s vs ~1.85s
# warm-after-grammar-edit (measured); the ~1.2s saving is below the
# test-run/corpus-sweep cycle noise and the `--connect` server carries
# an intermittent stale-synthesized-type silent-hang footgun on exactly
# the @:peg/@:build files every Phase-3 slice edits. Run protocol:
#   haxe test-js.hxml                       # compile only
#   ANYPARSE_HXFORMAT_FORK=… node bin/test.js   # run (env not via --cmd)
-cp src
-cp test
-lib utest
-lib hxnodejs
-main RunTests
-js bin/test.js
